<l>vēṟṟumai kuṟitta puṇarmoḻi nilaiyum</l>
<l>vēṟṟumai yalvaḻip puṇarmoḻi nilaiyu</l>
<l>meḻuttē cāriyai yāyiru paṇpi</l>
<l>ṉoḻukkal valiya puṇaruṅ kālai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Words whose fusion and accumulation</l>
<l>is sanctioned as <foreign xml:lang="ta">marūu</foreign> do also occur</l>
<l>in the situation of juxtaposition.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
